reviewText:
Okay so for those feeling sentimental and wanting some VHS tapes, this is a great deal.  Cases were included with all, no repeats.  I categorized them as follows:
Jackie Chan (9)
Sylvester Stallone (6)
Humphrey Bogart (6)
Charles Bronson (4)
Nicolas Cage (4)
Jack Lemmon (4)
John Candy (3)
Jim Carey (3)
Pierce Brosnan (3)
Arnold Schwarzenegger (2)
Dan Aykroyd (2)
Other (4)
